com.salesforce.omakase.parser.factory

Class BaseParserFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.salesforce.omakase.parser.factory.BaseParserFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParserFactory
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    StandardParserFactory

    public class BaseParserFactory
extends Object
implements ParserFactory
    Base class for ParserFactorys.

    Subclasses can override methods as appropriate to specify alternative parser implementations.
